cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is related to natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning, which are covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as it covers NLP and information retrieval (IR) topics. The paper also uses statistical models, which are covered by cs.LG (Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of Hidden Markov Models (HMMs) suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as a possible category.
